1. turn on these two feature :
	a. windows subsystem for linux
	b. virtual machine platform

2. install any linux distro from windows store

3. open cmd as admin
	- to list installed distros
	$ wsl -l

	- to show wsl verson running on each distro
	$ wsl -l -v

	- to change to wls 2 version
	$ wsl --set-version "distro name" 2

	- set default destro for wsl
	$ wsl -s "distro name"
	
	- set default install version 2 for any distro
	$ wsl --set-default-version 2


4. for more info run
	$ wsl --help
